### Offloading Long-Running Tasks to Job Queue (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/hooks/overview.mdx

Demonstrates how to offload long-running tasks from Payload CMS hooks to the jobs queue. This prevents blocking the request lifecycle and improves performance by allowing the request to complete while the task runs asynchronously in the background.

```typescript
{
  hooks: {
    afterChange: [
      async ({ doc, req }) => {
        // Offload to job queue
        await req.payload.jobs.queue(...)
        // ...
      },
    ],
  },
}
```

